#### Work Servers
## Prod
Host bastion
  Hostname 35.199.17.108
  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/google_compute_engine
  ControlPath ~/.ssh/bastion-%r@%h:%p.ctl
  ControlMaster auto
  ControlPersist 10m

Host azkaban-prod
  Hostname azkaban-us-central1-a.int.2pth.com
